{"tid":1559178,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"又係時候同大家重温一下，梁天琦曾經講過啲乜嘢","createTime":"2019-09-10T16:46:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T15:49:36.000Z","uid":23094,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"00a79f8d93e12247bcbc96a8448f3856c6d119cf","tid":1559178,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:46:37.000Z","msg":"我見有手足話最近淨係掛住唱歌，搞人鍊，屌Popo<br />\n冇啲正式啲抗爭行動，好似開始冷卻緊咁<br />\n其實我覺得每個行動都有佢自己嘅意義同價值<br />\n唔應該啱啱開始就咁快否定呢啲行動嘅作用<br />\n就算係已經被公認為「是沒用的」和平遊行<br />\n都一定仍然有佢嘅作用<br />\n<br />\n所以，我覺得有必要同大家重温一下梁天琦嘅演講<br />\n<br />\n1.<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋唔可以再繼續教條主義<br />\n邊一個方式可以推翻呢一個政府嘅<br />\n呢一個方式就應該要去做</span></span><br />\n我唔希望因為有人批評你哋嘅手段<br />\n結果就完全放棄你哋相信嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n唔好再繼續再教條主義<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再盲目相信自己嘅嗰一條道路<br />\n係一定會成功，係必須要行嘅道路<br />\n而其他嘅所有道路都係唔應該行，係錯嘅</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n如果呢個政府唔令你嘅革命失敗<br />\n唔打壓你嘅革命，唔令到你有犧牲<br />\n唔剝削你嘅權力，唔扼殺你哋係萌芽之中<br />\n代表啲乜嘢？<br />\n代表你哋嘅革命冇效囉<br />\n代表你對政府冇威脅囉<br />\n<br />\n咁所以，今時今日呢一個局面<br />\n好似好差，但同時間亦都反證一樣嘢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係我哋對香港政府以及北京政府、中國<br />\n我哋對佢哋構成威脅</span></span><br />\n所以大家係應該為呢件事出現而鼓舞<br />\n<br />\n3.<br />\n政府唔係一個管治人民嘅機構<br />\n政府應該係人民嘅僕人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人民唔應該害怕政府<br />\n政府應該害怕人民</span></span><br />\n<br />\n政府本身已經係一個暴力嘅機構<br />\n對住一個暴力嘅機構<br />\n我哋唔可以仁慈，唔可以懦弱<br />\n亦都唔可以再同佢哋講乜嘢仁義道德<br />\n呢一個政府根本就係一個無賴嘅政府，無賴嘅政權<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中國就係一無賴嘅國家<br />\n你同佢講仁義道德做乜鬼嘢呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n4.<br />\n革命本身係一樣乜嘢事呢？<br />\n革命本身就係講緊一個社會結構<br />\n權力分配，一個根本性嘅改變<br />\n一個從上而下嘅改變其實係代表一個改革<br />\n而一個從下而上嘅改變就係革命<br />\n<br />\n我哋唔可以再靠依個政府網開一面<br />\n因為如果你依靠佢網開一面先至俾我哋有民主嘅話<br />\n呢一種只不過係一種人治<br />\n點解我哋要當權者網開一面呢<br />\n我哋唔希望香港係一個人治嘅社會<br />\n我哋希望香港係一個法治嘅社會<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">憲法寫到明我哋應有嘅權利我哋就應該要有</span></span><br />\n<br />\n相信大家都知道佢（孫中山）喺1895年<br />\n成立咗興中會開始正式嘅革命<br />\n幾時先至成功？1911年<br />\n由佢開始走上革命嘅依條路，用咗16年<br />\n先至推翻到一個滿清政府<br />\n我唔想掃大家興，唔想潑大家冷水<br />\n但係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">革命係一條長嘅路</span></span><br />\n冇可能一時三刻就成功<br />\n但又有可能突然之間一時三刻就會成功<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋要保持依一個革命嘅精神<br />\n我哋要影響更加多嘅人<br />\n因為當成功嘅嗰一刻<br />\n我哋回望返過去就知道一切都係值得</span></span><br />\n得民心者得天下，所以我哋最先要做嘅嘢<br />\n係影響更加多嘅人<br />\n<br />\n5.<br />\n我知道如果我真係繼續半信半疑<br />\n而唔去做嘅話，我一定會失敗<br />\n如果我係秉持住呢一個夢想<br />\n即使知道好難成功，好大機會會失敗<br />\n即使知道我走出嚟會俾人恥笑，會俾人唾棄<br />\n會俾人謾罵，會被人打壓<br />\n但我都依然繼續去做<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要繼續保持一個夢想<br />\n終有一日我哋會成功</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黎明之前嘅黑暗，係至撚黑暗嘅<br />\n但係黎明即將會來臨</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VEUhAVki0DA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVEUhAVki0DA&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeReqQBVxexyTzYM5wEVuQb9nQ%3D&h=9885424f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VEUhAVki0DA</a>"},{"pid":"e4c09fbb95bcda74edc3222d7cca459f5cb45d8e","tid":1559178,"uid":128388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:51:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">915 12點英領 3點民陣</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b586f8aa8d006c2c9de3ac439b5837dcd6958883","tid":1559178,"uid":23094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:53:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一個人要代表嘅當然係代表佢自己<br />\n但同時間佢代表嘅只不過係一個理念<br />\n你哋追隨嘅應該係一個理念<br />\n而唔係一個人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請各位手足謹記前人嘅\b一字一句</span>"},{"pid":"191ebd1adfdf59c19801f582fbc1e32e34591a6a","tid":1559178,"uid":296491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:54:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要人！否則下一代玩完！政府想滅絕有腦既香港人！！！</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1559187/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1559187/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\np牌借位推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47baa1239fc0846077140cdb4fcea22b37d7f315","tid":1559178,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:57:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請各位手足謹記前人嘅\b一字一句</span>"},{"pid":"481e411fa79cad26c14235758db90da700cd3445","tid":1559178,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:58:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"92fea9c0450a77ed31cfb2aca31044df8615fccc","tid":1559178,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:01:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"4efed19fc61949dcdaec02fb84c2b58638959133","tid":1559178,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:04:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"868b3fc5847fb927358847d548a515e226776e7d","tid":1559178,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:05:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"3582b3367db1b23cfc28e3f303bc5e4b2637f067","tid":1559178,"uid":298570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:08:20.000Z","msg":"//我哋唔可以再靠依個政府網開一面<br />\n因為如果你依靠佢網開一面先至俾我哋有民主嘅話<br />\n呢一種只不過係一種人治<br />\n點解我哋要當權者網開一面呢<br />\n我哋唔希望香港係一個人治嘅社會<br />\n我哋希望香港係一個法治嘅社會//<br />\n<br />\n所以根本性係我地追求緊嘅五大訴求都係建基於我地仲相信制度，覺得值得投資時間相信，但係我地面對嘅大佬係全世界最喪嘅大佬，所以唯有完全的港人治港先可以解決呢個根本性問題。（雖然會有好強烈反彈，但係我地只可以相信同前行）"},{"pid":"22141b7a3894f9763a15bc633aa9632589c6e2df","tid":1559178,"uid":187194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:12:14.000Z","msg":"天琦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e9430e8eea2735b6667ed98cc6cbee44e9083c2","tid":1559178,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:12:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"9cc2aff36d6f399b0784afb8d3afc3e5d896a34f","tid":1559178,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:14:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"143ecc30fb4e52a3b29b9ea849bc040273b9defc","tid":1559178,"uid":252064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:14:37.000Z","msg":"冷咩卻<br />\n黎緊民陣<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月15號大遊行</span></span><br />\n記得出黎<br />\n抵制黨鐵 罷食藍絲店如吉野家<br />\n繼續文宣<br />\n始終大家要番學番工<br />\n主力集中星期六日都係好事"},{"pid":"1d2c8514809d58c232e3ea459981af3bc5bd4314","tid":1559178,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:15:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GiW8u64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGiW8u64.jpg&h=6e2a8a86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1558977\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1558977</a>"},{"pid":"16ca4faef9ee25620dcb8fb1f48fe1b415b92bfa","tid":1559178,"uid":132625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:16:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光</span></span>"},{"pid":"0bf3df8ee6e1d2f56c1f130ef8f9c482f742635d","tid":1559178,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:19:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"c8c4e3fda2aee2111105e4bce2d74e9805116d90","tid":1559178,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:24:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"3f318489922caa143e034c516e6f7664ae046b52","tid":1559178,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:26:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"1a55ab7b5377812af5ee12c9754611076d426381","tid":1559178,"uid":279976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47baa1239fc0846077140cdb4fcea22b37d7f315","tid":1559178,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:57:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請各位手足謹記前人嘅\b一字一句</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:38:01.000Z","msg":"你咁諗, 就已經係教條主義<br />\n梁天琦成個抗爭思想中心就係極度現實咁睇結果<br />\n<br />\n一開始咁多創意萌芽, 就係因為「兄弟爬山」<br />\n只要覺得自己做嘅嘢有用, 就去做, 大家見到呢樣嘢有用, 就一齊落手落腳支持。 登報, 圍稅局, 道歉, 不合作運動, 和你塞, 做任何事之前都無人知道結果。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好因為人地阻止而放棄唔去做, 同時應該檢視自己做嘅事對最終目標係近咗定係遠咗</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n你現在立即諗清楚, 香港人最終目標係咩?<br />\n圍繞呢個目標你可以做到D咩去幫助香港人去達成?<br />\n<br />\n好多人爭論「要打嬴怪物, 自己應唔應該變成怪物」<br />\n我話你知唔應該咁諗, 而係「為達到目標, 即使變成怪物, 亦義不容辭」<br />\n但係唔代表你應該立即變成一隻怪物<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>上善若水，水善利萬物而不爭，處為人之所惡，故幾於道。</strong></span></span><br />\nBe water 除教大家打游擊之外, 係教抗爭中唔同團體互相扶持之道, 善利萬物而不爭。除咗講緊前線延遲狗狗推進, 亦類似圍完稅局有手足去道歉恢復民意支持, 更加好似立法會當日煲底手足入會議廳救走死士。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">和勇不分, 互相扶持 先係前期運動真正成功之道</span></strong>"},{"pid":"c95321ea7d5f22f69b3d39897c66837cdbfe77c5","tid":1559178,"uid":119607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00a79f8d93e12247bcbc96a8448f3856c6d119cf","tid":1559178,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:46:37.000Z","msg":"我見有手足話最近淨係掛住唱歌，搞人鍊，屌Popo<br />\n冇啲正式啲抗爭行動，好似開始冷卻緊咁<br />\n其實我覺得每個行動都有佢自己嘅意義同價值<br />\n唔應該啱啱開始就咁快否定呢啲行動嘅作用<br />\n就算係已經被公認為「是沒用的」和平遊行<br />\n都一定仍然有佢嘅作用<br />\n<br />\n所以，我覺得有必要同大家重温一下梁天琦嘅演講<br />\n<br />\n1.<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋唔可以再繼續教條主義<br />\n邊一個方式可以推翻呢一個政府嘅<br />\n呢一個方式就應該要去做</span></span><br />\n我唔希望因為有人批評你哋嘅手段<br />\n結果就完全放棄你哋相信嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n唔好再繼續再教條主義<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再盲目相信自己嘅嗰一條道路<br />\n係一定會成功，係必須要行嘅道路<br />\n而其他嘅所有道路都係唔應該行，係錯嘅</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n如果呢個政府唔令你嘅革命失敗<br />\n唔打壓你嘅革命，唔令到你有犧牲<br />\n唔剝削你嘅權力，唔扼殺你哋係萌芽之中<br />\n代表啲乜嘢？<br />\n代表你哋嘅革命冇效囉<br />\n代表你對政府冇威脅囉<br />\n<br />\n咁所以，今時今日呢一個局面<br />\n好似好差，但同時間亦都反證一樣嘢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係我哋對香港政府以及北京政府、中國<br />\n我哋對佢哋構成威脅</span></span><br />\n所以大家係應該為呢件事出現而鼓舞<br />\n<br />\n3.<br />\n政府唔係一個管治人民嘅機構<br />\n政府應該係人民嘅僕人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人民唔應該害怕政府<br />\n政府應該害怕人民</span></span><br />\n<br />\n政府本身已經係一個暴力嘅機構<br />\n對住一個暴力嘅機構<br />\n我哋唔可以仁慈，唔可以懦弱<br />\n亦都唔可以再同佢哋講乜嘢仁義道德<br />\n呢一個政府根本就係一個無賴嘅政府，無賴嘅政權<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中國就係一無賴嘅國家<br />\n你同佢講仁義道德做乜鬼嘢呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n4.<br />\n革命本身係一樣乜嘢事呢？<br />\n革命本身就係講緊一個社會結構<br />\n權力分配，一個根本性嘅改變<br />\n一個從上而下嘅改變其實係代表一個改革<br />\n而一個從下而上嘅改變就係革命<br />\n<br />\n我哋唔可以再靠依個政府網開一面<br />\n因為如果你依靠佢網開一面先至俾我哋有民主嘅話<br />\n呢一種只不過係一種人治<br />\n點解我哋要當權者網開一面呢<br />\n我哋唔希望香港係一個人治嘅社會<br />\n我哋希望香港係一個法治嘅社會<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">憲法寫到明我哋應有嘅權利我哋就應該要有</span></span><br />\n<br />\n相信大家都知道佢（孫中山）喺1895年<br />\n成立咗興中會開始正式嘅革命<br />\n幾時先至成功？1911年<br />\n由佢開始走上革命嘅依條路，用咗16年<br />\n先至推翻到一個滿清政府<br />\n我唔想掃大家興，唔想潑大家冷水<br />\n但係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">革命係一條長嘅路</span></span><br />\n冇可能一時三刻就成功<br />\n但又有可能突然之間一時三刻就會成功<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋要保持依一個革命嘅精神<br />\n我哋要影響更加多嘅人<br />\n因為當成功嘅嗰一刻<br />\n我哋回望返過去就知道一切都係值得</span></span><br />\n得民心者得天下，所以我哋最先要做嘅嘢<br />\n係影響更加多嘅人<br />\n<br />\n5.<br />\n我知道如果我真係繼續半信半疑<br />\n而唔去做嘅話，我一定會失敗<br />\n如果我係秉持住呢一個夢想<br />\n即使知道好難成功，好大機會會失敗<br />\n即使知道我走出嚟會俾人恥笑，會俾人唾棄<br />\n會俾人謾罵，會被人打壓<br />\n但我都依然繼續去做<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要繼續保持一個夢想<br />\n終有一日我哋會成功</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黎明之前嘅黑暗，係至撚黑暗嘅<br />\n但係黎明即將會來臨</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VEUhAVki0DA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVEUhAVki0DA&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeReqQBVxexyTzYM5wEVuQb9nQ%3D&h=9885424f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VEUhAVki0DA</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:43:33.000Z","msg":"諷刺嘅係林鄭先係令香港人醒覺啲關鍵一人。"},{"pid":"09b2b7efc4a66c134b6a678ce966a022999ef1b3","tid":1559178,"uid":67786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:45:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">天琦：搵份hea工，練好結他，唔駛買樓，夠生活就夠</span></span>"},{"pid":"a46f47d1b346be41ea058676ff2b4f6df75651ba","tid":1559178,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T23:40:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"f41378edc9834a23cb1897516f7bd1f3357487db","tid":1559178,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T23:43:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但天琦從頭到尾都係支持勇武抗爭，依家咁多唱歌嘉年華又係天琦樂見嘅野？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc1d38de4e9552de10d4da08b39a6419d221094","tid":1559178,"uid":20372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T23:45:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}